"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-boycott-have-your-say-video\", \"text\": \"ByBen Chapman,  Published: 29/07/2024  Updated: 29/07/2024  After many viewers furiously switched off the Paris Olympics opening ceremony over its supposed depiction of Leonardo Da Vinci's 'The Last Supper' painting, we are asking whether you would consider going a step further and boycott the whole event.  Organisers have rushed to apologise over the act which GB News host Bev Turner said was \\\"utterly depraved\\\".  COMMENT NOW - Are you boycotting the Paris Olympics?\"}"